      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i really dont think it's that serious if it doesn't ache. i have some ibuprofen and some ear drops at home, can i just take those and wait a few days to see if the hearing comes back? i'm in oslo and finding an ent specialist right now sounds like a huge hassle.",
